William Baldwin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/William_Baldwin 0 William Joseph Baldwin (born February 21, 1963) is an American actor, producer and writer. A member of the Baldwin family, he is the second-youngest of the four Baldwin brothers. He has starred in the films Flatliners (1990), Backdraft (1991), The Squid and the Whale (2005), and played himself in Forgetting Sarah Marshall. Baldwin is married to singer Chynna Phillips.
